たとえばゆるい幸せが
For example, if a relaxed happiness

573
00:47:17,940 --> 00:47:23,140
だらっと続いたとする
were to drag on continuously,

574
00:47:23,440 --> 00:47:28,640
きっと悪い種が芽を出して<
surely a bad seed would sprout...

575
