We were jamming during a lesson and thought, "Wow, isn't this super cool?"

593
00:49:45,140 --> 00:49:49,140
「先生もよかったら一緒に弾いてくれませんか？」って言って、
So I asked, "Teacher, would you like to play along with me?"

594
00:49:49,140 --> 00:49:52,140
