00:54:53,615 --> 00:55:00,115
数量限定ではないので、ぜひね、あの、ゆっくり購入していただけるととっても嬉しいです。よろしくお願いします。
They aren't limited in quantity, so I'd be very happy if you could take your time to purchase them. Thank you!

672
00:55:00,163 --> 00:55:01,463
おねがいします
Please!

673
00:55:01,463 --> 00:55:05,963
そして、皆様待望のお知らせがございます！
And now, we have an announcement you've all been waiting for!

674
00:55:05,963 --> 00:55:07,663
こちら！
This is it!

675
00:55:08,163 --> 00:55:13,163
なんと！凛堂千早ソロとして、初めてのオリ曲
Believe it or not, my very first solo original song as Rindo Chihaya,

676
00:55:13,163 --> 00:55:18,663
「Flatout」がこの後24時、7月9日木曜日の0時
"Flatout," will be digitally released later tonight at midnight,

677
00:55:18,663 --> 00:55:23,163
この後ですね、3時間ちょい後くらいからデジタルリリースされます！
well, technically at 0:00 on Thursday, July 9th, which is about 3 hours from now!

678
00:55:23,163 --> 00:55:25,663
やったー！
Yay!

679
00:55:26,663 --> 00:55:33,163
このポーズしてる。今回のライブのタイトルにもなっている「Flatout」は、オリ曲のタイトルでございました！
I'm doing this pose. "Flatout," which is also the title of this live stream, was the title of my original song!

680
00:55:34,163 --> 00:55:40,163
えー、この配信が終わった後にMVが公開されますので、そちらもぜひお楽しみに！
The MV will be released after this stream ends, so please look forward to it!

681
00:55:40,163 --> 00:55:46,663
概要欄にね、あの、そのうち多分リンクが貼られたり貼られなかったりすると思うので、そちらもチェックしてみてください。
I think a link will probably be added to the description box sooner or later, so please check it out too.

682
00:55:47,163 --> 00:55:52,663
えー新曲、この後やっぱり早速聴きたいですよね？この後、披露するので絶対に聴いてください。
Now, I'm sure you want to hear the new song right away, don't you? I'll be performing it next, so please make sure to listen to it.

683
00:55:52,663 --> 00:55:56,663
最後まで、最後までね、チャンネルはそのままで見ていってくださいね。
Please stay tuned until the very end, and keep your channel right here.

684
00:55:57,163 --> 00:56:02,663
以上、凛堂千早生誕祭2026のグッズ情報とリリース情報でした！
And that's all for the merchandise and release information for Rindo Chihaya's Birthday Festival 2026!

685
00:56:02,663 --> 00:56:06,663
みんな、買ってね！サブスクでも聴いてね！
Everyone, please buy them! And make sure to stream the song too!

686
00:56:07,663 --> 00:56:10,163
はい、ということで、怒涛のお知らせコーナーでした。
Alright, so that was the whirlwind of announcements.

687
00:56:10,163 --> 00:56:14,163
ここからいよいよライブもクライマックスです。でも、まだまだあります。
From here on, the live performance is finally reaching its climax. But there is still more to come.

688
00:56:14,163 --> 00:56:19,163
盛り上がる準備できてますか？最後一緒にぶち上げていこうね！
Are you ready to get hyped? Let's blow the roof off together at the end!

689
00:56:19,663 --> 00:56:21,663
では、準備してきます。
Now, I'll go get ready.

690
00:56:21,663 --> 00:56:24,163
会おう！そのチャンネルはそのままに。
See you! Keep your channel right here.

691
00:56:52,663 --> 00:56:54,163
I wanna fly so high

692
00:56:54,163 --> 00:56:56,663
Yeah, I know my wings are dried

693
00:56:57,163 --> 00:57:00,163
「翼仰げば」って人は云う
People say, "Just look up at the wings"

694
00:57:00,163 --> 00:57:03,663
その向こうにあるは無情
But what lies beyond is heartlessness

695
00:57:04,163 --> 00:57:06,663
飛べる者 落ちる者
Those who can fly, those who fall

696
00:57:07,163 --> 00:57:10,663
誰も見てない 気にも留めない
No one is watching, no one even cares

697
00:57:11,163 --> 00:57:13,663
それでも飛び続けた
Yet I kept on flying

698
00:57:14,163 --> 00:57:20,663
傷ついた言葉乗せ 運びたいから
Because I want to carry and deliver these wounded words

699
00:57:21,163 --> 00:57:24,163
追いかけて届くよう
Chasing, hoping to reach you

700
00:57:24,163 --> 00:57:28,663
僕等 一心に羽ばたいて
We flap our wings with all our heart

701
00:57:29,163 --> 00:57:32,163
問いかけて嘆いた夜
The night I questioned and lamented

702
00:57:32,163 --> 00:57:35,663
故郷（まち）は一層輝いて
My hometown shined even brighter

703
00:57:36,163 --> 00:57:43,163
ワタリドリの様に今 旅に立つよ
Now I set out on a journey like a migratory bird

704
00:57:43,163 --> 00:57:50,163
ありもしないストーリーを 描いてみせるよ
A story that doesn't even exist, I will show you I can draw it

705
00:57:56,663 --> 00:57:58,663
I wanna fly so far

706
00:57:58,663 --> 00:58:00,663
Away with my guitar

707
00:58:01,163 --> 00:58:04,163
「一人じゃない」って人々は歌う
People sing, "You're not alone"

708
00:58:04,163 --> 00:58:07,663
間違いじゃない 理想論でもない
It's not wrong, nor is it just an ideal theory

709
00:58:07,663 --> 00:58:10,663
ただ頼って生きたくはない
I just don't want to live by relying on others

710
00:58:11,163 --> 00:58:14,163
誰も聴いていない 気にも留めない
No one is listening, no one even cares

711
00:58:14,163 --> 00:58:17,663
それでも歌い続けた
Yet I kept on singing

712
00:58:18,163 --> 00:58:24,163
傷ついたあなたを 笑わせたいから
Because I want to make you, who are hurt, smile

713
00:58:25,163 --> 00:58:28,163
追い風届けるよ
I will deliver a tailwind to you

714
00:58:29,163 --> 00:58:32,163
僕等 一心に羽ばたいて
We flap our wings with all our heart

715
00:58:32,163 --> 00:58:36,163
遠い過去を背負ってた
I will carry you, who were burdened with a distant past,

716
00:58:36,163 --> 00:58:39,663
あなたを未来へ運ぶよ
to the future

717
00:58:40,163 --> 00:58:47,163
ワタリドリの様に今 群れをなして
Now like a migratory bird, we form a flock

718
00:58:47,163 --> 00:58:55,163
大それた四重奏を 奏で終える日まで
Until the day we finish playing this grand quartet

719
00:59:08,663 --> 00:59:11,163
All this time we come and we grow

720
00:59:11,163 --> 00:59:14,163
Now it's time that we should go

721
00:59:14,163 --> 00:59:17,663
But we both know that this is for sure

722
00:59:17,663 --> 00:59:21,163
It's not the end of the world

723
00:59:21,163 --> 00:59:23,663
We'll see you one day

724
00:59:29,663 --> 00:59:32,163
追いかけて届くよう
Chasing, hoping to reach you

725
00:59:32,163 --> 00:59:36,163
僕等 一心に羽ばたいて
We flap our wings with all our heart

726
00:59:36,163 --> 00:59:39,663
問いかけて嘆いた夜
The night I questioned and lamented

727
00:59:39,663 --> 00:59:43,663
朝焼け色に染まっていく
It's being dyed in the colors of the morning glow

728
00:59:44,163 --> 00:59:51,163
ワタリドリの様にいつか 舞い戻るよ
Like a migratory bird, one day I will fly back

729
00:59:51,163 --> 00:59:55,163
ありもしないストーリーを
A story that doesn't even exist

730
00:59:55,163 --> 01:00:00,163
いつかまた会う日まで
Until the day we meet again

731
01:00:00,138 --> 01:00:02,438
...いつかまた会う日まで
...until the day we meet again

732
01:01:03,138 --> 01:01:15,138
Shiny Smily Story (2022 ver.)
作詞：金丸佳史 作曲：中野領太 編曲：秋浦智裕
Shiny Smily Story (2022 ver.)
Lyrics: Yoshifumi Kanemaru / Composition: Ryota Nakano / Arrangement: Tomohiro Akiura

733
01:05:16,186 --> 01:05:17,486
はい、ということで
So, anyway...

734
01:05:17,486 --> 01:05:22,686
輪堂千速生誕祭、ここまで見てくれたみんな本当にありがとうございます！
Thank you so much to everyone who has watched Chihaya Rindo's Birthday Festival up to this point!

735
01:05:23,186 --> 01:05:25,886
えー、次が本当にラストの曲です。
So, next up is indeed the last song.

736
01:05:26,286 --> 01:05:31,386
この曲はいつかみんなと現地で会って、
I hoped that we could sing this song at the very end when we eventually meet in person...

737
01:05:31,386 --> 01:05:35,486
ライブができた時に最後に歌えたらいいなって、そんな思いで、千速のいろんな気持ちを込めて作ってもらった曲です。
...and have a live concert, so it was made with many of Chihaya's feelings in mind.

738
01:05:35,486 --> 01:05:37,886
千速の初めてのオリ曲、聴いてください。
Please listen to Chihaya's very first original song.

739
01:05:38,186 --> 01:05:41,186
Flat out。
\"Flat out\".

740
01:05:46,386 --> 01:05:49,686
メランコリーのリフレイン 午前三時
A melancholy refrain at 3 AM.

741
01:05:49,686 --> 01:05:56,686
夢を見るには少し遅すぎたMidnight
Midnight was a little too late to dream.

742
01:05:57,386 --> 01:06:00,986
言葉にならないままの想いが
Before the feelings that won't turn into words...

743
01:06:00,986 --> 01:06:03,386
溢れだしてしまう前に
...start to overflow,

744
01:06:03,386 --> 01:06:05,286
飛び出した部屋
I ran out of my room,

745
01:06:05,286 --> 01:06:07,986
光を見たくて
wanting to see the light.

746
01:06:08,186 --> 01:06:13,786
”どうせ”だなんて何度だって諦めようとしたって
Even if I tried to give up over and over again, saying \"it's useless anyway,\"

747
01:06:13,986 --> 01:06:19,586
だけどきっと今日もそっと伸ばした手 あの星まで
I surely stretched my hand out gently to that star again today.

748
01:06:19,986 --> 01:06:25,686
自分さえだませない嘘はもうやめて踏み込め
Stop the lies that can't even fool yourself, and take a step forward!

749
01:06:28,186 --> 01:06:33,886
駆け抜けて 音も風も抜き去って
Run through, passing the sound and the wind,

750
01:06:33,986 --> 01:06:39,686
迷いさえも振り切ってスピードを上げて
shaking off even the hesitation, speed up!

751
01:06:39,786 --> 01:06:44,986
行かなくちゃ 夜のまだその向こうへ
I must go, beyond the night,

752
01:06:44,986 --> 01:06:47,586
見たこともない世界へ
to a world I've never seen,

753
01:06:47,586 --> 01:06:49,886
今最高速度で
now at top speed,

754
01:06:49,886 --> 01:06:51,786
高鳴る方へ
towards the thrumming!

755
01:06:52,186 --> 01:06:57,486
答えなんてなくたってただこうしていたいだけ
Even if there's no answer, I just want to stay like this,

756
01:06:57,586 --> 01:07:03,686
未完成で完全な道の先まで 行ける信じて
believing I can go to the end of this imperfect, perfect road.

757
01:07:24,386 --> 01:07:28,686
差し障りないように生きた日々
In the days lived to be harmless,

758
01:07:28,886 --> 01:07:34,686
諦めの言い訳を探すのをやめて保存しよう
stop looking for excuses to give up.

759
01:07:35,186 --> 01:07:39,586
もどかしい気持ち 窓の向こうに
Frustrating feelings, beyond the window,

760
01:07:39,686 --> 01:07:45,486
輝くあの星みたいになりたかったんだ
I wanted to become like that shining star.

761
01:07:45,886 --> 01:07:50,986
足りない物だらけだって どれだけ離されたって
Even if I'm full of missing things, no matter how far I'm separated,

762
01:07:51,186 --> 01:07:53,786
止まればそこまでなんだ
if I stop, that's it!

763
01:07:53,886 --> 01:07:56,686
進め 進め
Go forward, go forward!

764
01:07:56,886 --> 01:08:02,186
未来を変える瞬間はいつかじゃなくて今なんだ
The moment to change the future is not someday, it's now!

765
01:08:02,186 --> 01:08:05,186
進め 進め
Go forward, go forward,

766
01:08:05,186 --> 01:08:08,186
先へ さあ
ahead, now!

767
01:08:17,186 --> 01:08:20,786
もっと遠くまで
Even further...

768
01:08:25,186 --> 01:08:28,686
確かめに行くんだ Flat out
...I will go to find out, Flat out!

769
01:08:28,986 --> 01:08:34,186
駆け抜けて 夢に見たその舞台へ
Run through, to that stage I saw in my dreams,

770
01:08:34,186 --> 01:08:39,686
決して振り返らないでスピードを上げて保存しよう
never looking back, speed up!

771
01:08:39,786 --> 01:08:44,986
行かなくちゃ 夜のまだその向こうへ保存しよう
I must go, beyond the night,

772
01:08:44,986 --> 01:08:47,586
見たこともない世界へ
to a world I've never seen,

773
01:08:47,586 --> 01:08:49,886
今最高速度で保存しよう
now at top speed,

774
01:08:49,886 --> 01:08:51,786
信じる方へ
towards what I believe!

775
01:08:52,186 --> 01:08:57,486
答えなんてなくたってただこうして
Even if there's no answer, just like this,

776
01:08:57,586 --> 01:09:00,186
走り出したんだ 止まらないよ さあ
I started running, I won't stop, now!

777
01:09:00,186 --> 01:09:06,686
あの星に届け
reach that star!

778
01:09:11,986 --> 01:09:16,986
輪堂千速生誕祭2026 見ていただいて本当にありがとうございました！
Thank you so much for watching Chihaya Rindo's Birthday Festival 2026!

779
01:09:17,186 --> 01:09:20,886
これからもみんなと向こうの景色たくさん見に行きたいです！
From now on, I want to go see many sights beyond with everyone!

780
01:09:20,986 --> 01:09:24,186
これからも千速のことを好きでいてついてきてくれたら嬉しいです！
I'd be happy if you keep loving Chihaya and follow along!

781
01:09:24,186 --> 01:09:27,686
本当に今日はありがとうございましたー！
Thank you so much for today!

782
01:09:27,686 --> 01:09:31,186
ありがとうねー！
Thank you!

783
01:10:01,161 --> 01:10:06,161
輪堂千夜生誕LIVE お越しいただきありがとうございます
[Text: Thank you for coming to Rindo Chiyah's Birthday LIVE!]

784
01:10:06,161 --> 01:10:11,161
これからも走り続けるよ！！！ 今日は本当にありがとう
[Text: I will keep running forward! Thank you so much for today!]

785
01:10:11,361 --> 01:10:14,661
揺れる境界線
The swaying boundary line

786
01:10:14,961 --> 01:10:18,461
僕らを繋ぎ止めて
holds us together.

787
01:10:18,761 --> 01:10:22,161
あの日の誓いも
Will even the vow from that day

788
01:10:22,461 --> 01:10:27,661
いつしか色褪せていくの？
eventually fade away?

789
01:10:30,361 --> 01:10:33,661
音も立てずに
Without making a sound,

790
01:10:33,961 --> 01:10:37,361
崩れ去る世界で
in this crumbling world,

791
01:10:37,661 --> 01:10:41,161
確かなものなんて
I used to think there wasn't

792
01:10:41,361 --> 01:10:46,661
何一つ無いと思ってた
a single certain thing.

793
01:10:46,861 --> 01:10:48,961
だけど君が
But because you...

794
01:10:49,161 --> 01:10:52,661
手を伸ばしてくれたから
reached out your hand to me,

795
01:10:52,861 --> 01:10:56,361
もう一度だけ
just once more,

796
01:10:56,661 --> 01:11:02,661
信じてみようと思えたんだ
I felt like I could believe again.

